initializeTask

public void initializeTask()
Performs any necessary initialization for this task and optionally sends an expected value to a behavior class. For example, if this task is set to wait for the WINCH_IN_POSITION status, initializeTask() will call RobotClimb.setWinchTarget() with the value given to this task's constructor.
